---
title: Flow 2 - Sync and Read
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant W as Workers
    participant F as FastAPI
    participant G as Git
    participant H as hledger

    User->>W: POST /api/sync
    W->>F: POST /sync
    F->>G: git pull
    G-->>F: ok
    F-->>W: synced + timestamp
    W-->>User: timestamp shown

    User->>W: GET /api/balance
    W->>F: GET /balance
    F->>H: balance --json
    H-->>F: JSON
    F-->>W: JSON
    W-->>User: render view
